Interface RestDispatcherController

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EntryPoint
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractRestDispatcherController

    public interface RestDispatcherController
extends EntryPoint
    This interface is used to initiate the generation of RestServices and RestActions.

    Making it an EntryPoint makes sure GWT kicks off the generation as early as possible.
